{"tid":2362173,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"邱騰華：資金持續流入證明黨安法不影響外資信心","createTime":"2021-01-11T09:08:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T22:18:19.000Z","uid":21470,"like":12,"dislike":92,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"1d8d7d123afd41d68b443a67012b636f7eaf1942","tid":2362173,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T09:08:40.000Z","msg":"邱騰華：資金持續流入香港表明國安法不影響投資者信心<br />\n<br />\n商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華表示，在香港的國際企業將法治和治安視為作出投資的關鍵，對於有擔憂實施港區國安法會打擊商業環境，他接受《路透社》訪問時說，資金持續流入的事實表明，投資者對香港作為全球金融中心充滿信心。<br />\n<br />\n對於有商會和貿易組織對港區國安法實施，令香港更接近中國的專制制度，增加不確定性提出擔憂，邱騰華指出，在任何的商業活動，尤其是金融中心，人們會全面看待事物，而法治及治安是非常重要的一環。<br />\n<br />\n邱騰華又指出，新型肺炎疫情造成不明朗，即使當局計劃為全民注射疫苗，疫情亦不可能一下子解決。而目前難以預計與新加坡的「旅遊氣泡」計劃何時恢復。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569800-20210111.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569800-20210111.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BY%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=9ddbe9c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569800-20210111.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=172334cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569800-20210111.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"b9a33f6fadff325bc42105bbe7283276fbb13bbb","tid":2362173,"uid":51271,"like":70,"dislike":3,"score":67,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T09:09:36.000Z","msg":"關稅華，銀行存款下跌喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f306be47bd768f05f9ee071eda8c62234d1dcff0","tid":2362173,"uid":224533,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T09:10:17.000Z","msg":"冇腐乳，扣佢五十分"},{"pid":"6c665cfefa0d3108b2483995744bcb315120339b","tid":2362173,"uid":7